            <thetext>IS:

When the Generator&#39;s watch-job is started, the target command is not executed by default.  Changes that have been made before the watch-job are not recognized by the watch-job. 

SHOULD:

The possibility to trigger the target command on watch-job&#39;s start-up would be helpful. This means that every watched file is assumed as &quot;changed&quot; on watch-job startup.</thetext>
